{"tid":735773,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得其實唔會有人真正鐘意自己","createTime":"2018-07-09T17:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T14:16:39.000Z","uid":66753,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e84dda4a6cf77116bbdd133a267217385b92d822","tid":735773,"uid":66753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:47:42.000Z","msg":"矛盾撚入嚟圍下爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日都喺嫌棄自己同自我嘅鐘擺上拉扯<br />\n好憎自己柒同唔討好嘅一面<br />\n另一方面又會幾自我 想過到decent嘅生活 好似其他女咁 同到鐘意嘅人一齊<br />\n但係又會覺得 呢刻嘅自己根本冇人會真正鐘意<br />\n就算之前畀冇乜feel嘅人表過白<br />\n都只覺得佢係傻豬畀自己喺social media 塑造出嚟嘅形象或係相處時嘅表層呃咗<br />\n只要識耐啲 外表同內裡嘅原形畢露時就會被嫌棄<br />\n<br />\n屌 如本性是這麼低等 怎跟你相襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5beca69d78ab8b6b1885daa34e05f8fa2523b4a","tid":735773,"uid":177089,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:50:31.000Z","msg":"點都會有個人 唔埋你係一個點樣嘅人都鍾意你<br />\n<br />\nyou are always perfect for someone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6311aa8f50d84b076a345376cd7a022d18a8316f","tid":735773,"uid":160132,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:50:55.000Z","msg":"有人鍾意都只係比自己塑嶄造出嚟嘅形象吸引<br />\n覺得佢地根本就唔了解真實嘅自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地睇到social media 入面嘅自己好開心好活潑咁<br />\n但事實上係一條負能量到爆嘅頹撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4870d81cd4676ce2abeba29ea88b9220902a7d90","tid":735773,"uid":61173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:51:01.000Z","msg":"等左好多年<br />\n都未出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d23a76b59a10e8ae6626905119cca712d04662","tid":735773,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:51:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16d1832af7f3f6a463f91c0bbb4f4b3ac80bd616","tid":735773,"uid":66753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p